ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Working with Mary at the YPDC is a great first clinical experience. I would highly recommend it as a very supported space for developing clinical skills.
I would definitely recommend this practicum to other students, especially those in their second year.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Conducting clinical work has given me greater insight into how psychopathology can develop and manifest in different individuals. Working with patients has given me insight into the types of questions I'd like to ask in my research
This practicum has been an extremely valuable way to learn how to do clinical work.
